          "id": "f73f3ece8bbf1151b275dd9edb5817cb57bae326",
          "message": "chore: release v0.11.0 (#104)\n\n* chore: release v0.11.0\n\n* docs(changelog): record lru 0.16 -> 0.17 requirement change in v0.11.0\n\nThe lru bump landed only in [workspace.dependencies], so release-plz could\nnot attribute it to a package — but mssql-client inherits it, making the\npublished requirement change user-visible.\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: praxiomlabs-release-plz[bot] <290922893+praxiomlabs-release-plz[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>\nCo-authored-by: Justin Kindrix <jkindrix@gmail.com>",
